gurmukhi: ਅਸੰਭ ਰੂਪ ਅਨਭੈ ਪ੍ਰਭਾ ਅਤਿ ਬਲਿਸਟ ਜਲਿ ਥਲਿ ਕਰਣ ॥
transliteration: Asanbh Roop Anbhai Prabhaa At(i) Balist Jal(i) Thal(i) Karan||
translation: He is an Unborn Entity, His Glory is manifested through knowledge, He is most powerful and cause of the creation of water and land.

gurmukhi: ਅਚੁਤ ਅਨੰਤ ਅਦ੍ਵੈ ਅਮਿਤ ਨਾਥ ਨਿਰੰਜਨ ਤਵ ਸਰਣ ॥੧॥੩੨॥
transliteration: Achout Anant Advai Amit Naath Niranjan Tav Saran||1||32||
translation: He is imperishable, boundless, Non-dual, Unlimited and the Transcendent Lord, I am in Thy Refuge. 1 .32

gurmukhi: ਅਚੁਤ ਅਭੈ ਅਭੇਦ ਅਮਿਤ ਅਾਖੰਡ ਅਤੁਲ ਬਲ ॥
transliteration: Achout Abhai Abhed Amit Aakhannddprabal Dal||
translation: He is imperishable, boundless, Non-dual, Unlimited, Indivisible, and hath Unweighable Strenght.

gurmukhi: ਅਟਲ ਅਨੰਤ ਅਨਾਦਿ ਅਖੈ ਅਾਖੰਡ ਪ੍ਰਬਲ ਦਲ ॥
transliteration: Atal Anant Anaadh Akhai Aakhannddprabal Dal||
translation: He is Eternal, Infinite, Beginningless, Indivisible, and Master of Mighty forces.

gurmukhi: ਅਮਿਤ ਅਮਿਤ ਅਨਤੋਲ ਅਭੂ ਅਨਭੇਦ ਅਭੰਜਨ ॥
transliteration: Amit Amit Antol Abhoo Anbhed Abhanjan||
translation: He is Limits Boundless, Unweighable, elementless, indiscriminated and Invincible.

gurmukhi: ਅਨਬਿਕਾਰ ਅਾਤਮ ਸਰੂਪ ਸੁਰ ਨਰ ਮੁਨਿ ਰੰਜਨ ॥
transliteration: Anbikaar Aatam Saroopsur Nar Mounndi) Ranjan||
translation: He is Spiritual Entity without vices, pleasing to gods, men and sages.

gurmukhi: ਅਬਿਕਾਰ ਰੂਪ ਅਨ ਭੈ ਸਦਾ ਮੁਨਿ ਜਨ ਗਨ ਬੰਦਤ ਚਰਨ ॥
transliteration: Abikaar Roop An Bhai Sadaa Mounndi) Jan Gad Bandat Charan||
translation: He is and Entity without vices, always Fearless, the assemblies of sages and men bow at His Feet.

gurmukhi: ਭਵ ਭਰਨ ਕਰਨ ਦੁਖ ਦੋਖ ਹਰਨ ਅਤਿ ਪ੍ਰਤਾਪ ਭਰਮ ਭੈ ਹਰਨ ॥੨॥੩੩॥
transliteration: Bhav Bharan Karan Doukh Dokh Harab At(i) Prataap Bharam Bhai Haran||2||33||
translation: He pervades the world, removes the sufferings and blemishes, Supremely Glorious and effacer of illusions and fears.2.33.

gurmukhi: ਮੁਖ ਮੰਡਲ ਪਰ ਲਸਤ ਜੋਤਿ ੳੁਦੇਤ ਅਮਿਤ ਗਤ ॥
transliteration: Moukh Mandal Par Lasat Jot(i) Outot Amit Gad||
translation: On his facial sphere glistens the brilliant light of infinite movement.

gurmukhi: ਜਟਲ ਜੋਤ ਜਗਮਗਤ ਲਜਤ ਲਖ ਕੋਟਿ ਨਿਖਤਿ ਪਤਿ ॥
transliteration: Jatal Jot Jagmagad Lajat Lakh Kottee Nikhat(i) Pat(i)||
translation: Such is the setting and illumination of that Light that lakhs and millions of moon feel shy before it.

gurmukhi: ਚਕ੍ਵਰਤੀ ਚਕ੍ਵੈ ਚਕ੍ਰਤ ਚੳੁ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ ਕਰਿ ਧਰਿ ॥
transliteration: Chakravartichakravai Chakrat Chau Chakkra Kar(i) Dhar(i)||
translation: He carries the four corners of the world on His hand and thus the universal monarchs are amazed.

gurmukhi: ਪਦਮ ਨਾਥ ਪਦਮਾਛ ਨਵਲ ਨਾਰਾੲਿਣ ਨਰਹਰਿ ॥
transliteration: Padam Naath Padamaachh Naval Naaraain Narhar(i)||
translation: The Ever-new Lord with lotus-eyes, He is the Lord of men.
